        ‘INVITE A FRIEND’ SCHEME
        <ol type=""i"">
            <li>For every successful entrant that you have invited to The UFP, you get £1 discount, providing all terms and conditions are adhered to.</li>
            <li>Maximum discount this season from this offer is £10.</li>
            <li>Each friend you invite to The UFP must nominate you as their inviter in the designated box on their entry.</li>
