        </ol>
    </li>
    <li>
        ENTRY CONDITIONS
        <ol type=""i"">
            <li>Entrants may not submit multiple entries.</li>
            <li>The UFP does not permit group names as entries.</li>
            <li>All entries and payments must be completed by 31st July 2019.</li>
        </ol>
    </li>
