        <ol type=""i"">
            <li>All UFP entrants must have a valid email address. This is to be submitted in the relevant box on the entry. As this is our only way of contacting entrants (for updates, payments, amendments, etc.), an entry that is submitted without a valid email address will be cancelled and payment will be refunded, if possible.</li>
            <li>Email addresses will only be used for The UFP purposes, and will not be shared with third parties (see GDPR).</li>
            <li>Those who are receiving emails from The UFP may stop these emails at any time, by sending the word 'STOP'; however, their email address will remain on The UFP’s database until the end of the season.</li>
