        LEGAL
        <ol type=""i"">
            <li>The UFP is not a lottery or gaming activity, as a lottery or a gaming activity requires the winner to succeed wholly on chance. In The UFP, entrants exercise judgement when submitting their predictions. This is according to S14(5) Gambling Act 2005.</li>
            <li>The UFP does not currently run in order to provide personal financial gain for its owner. Legally speaking, The UFP is a non-commercial society. This is according to S19(1)(c) Gambling Act 2005.</li>
